                        <xs:documentation source="AdditionalRequirements">
                           <ns1:u>Required Documentation:</ns1:u>
                           <ns1:line1/>
                            CF2R-MCH-01-E - Space Conditioning Systems 
                           <ns1:line1/>
                             - Duct insulation requirement for the new portions of supply-air and return-air ducts or plenums: R6 (CZ 3, 5-7) and R8 (CZ 1, 2, 4, 8-16) 
                           <ns1:line1/>
                            CF2R and CF3R-MCH-20-H Duct Leakage Test required 
                           <ns1:line1/>
                             - Leakage rate compliance: less than or equal to 5 percent. 
                           <ns1:line1/>
                            CF2R and CF3R-MCH-22 Fan Efficacy 
                           <ns1:line1/>
                            CF2R and CF3R-MCH-23 Airflow Rate 
                           <ns1:line1/>
                            - Compliance: Fan Efficacy less than or equal to 0.58 W/cfm for non-gas furnaces and System Airflow greater than or equal to 350 cfm per ton.
                           <ns1:line1/>
                            - Alternative Compliance: CF2R and CF3R-MCH-28 Return Duct Design verification is an alternative to MCH-22 and MCH-23 verification. 
                           <ns1:line1/>
                            CF2R and CF3R-MCH-25-H Refrigerant Charge verification required when refrigerant containing components are installed or altered (applicable in CZ 2, 8-15).
                           <ns1:line1/>
                             
                           <ns1:u>Note:</ns1:u>
