                                             <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">If F08 ResidentialHvacCoolingComponentType ==  NoCoolingComponents, then result = N/A stored in NotApplicableMessage, Else choices are EER2, EER2SEER2, CEER.</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                          
