                                             <xs:documentation source="FieldText">Cooling Minimum Efficiency Value SEER/SEER2</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                             
                                             <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">If F08= no cooling component altered, then value =N/A; 
                                                Else user enter SEER2 value:  xx.x;  default minimum value for EER2/SEER2=13.4;
                                                Allow user to overwrite default value, but flag non-default values and report in project status notes field;</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                          
