                                             <xs:documentation source="CalculationsAndRules">If B04_DuctedSystem== false. result is N/A stored in NotApplicableMessage; Else   If A09_ClimateZone == 3, 5, 6 Or 7, then result = R6. Else If A09_ClimateZone == 1,2, 4 Or InRange(8, 16) result = R8 End If</xs:documentation>
                                             
                                          
